Ungoogled chromium is a collection of patches that remove Google
integration, tune privacy settings and remove blobs from source
code.

To enable hardware acceleration for video decode add the following flag
to your `/etc/chromium/default` file:

  CHROMIUM_FLAGS=" --enable-features=VaapiVideoDecoder "

Then check if it was enabled by visiting: chrome://gpu/ .

For more help with ungoogled-chromium please visit:
https://ungoogled-software.github.io/
